{"word":"G2576 - καμμύω - kammýō - kam-moo'-o - Close","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καμμύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kammýō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kam-moo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Close</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கண்களை மூடு"},{"paragraph":"to shut the eyes, close the eyes"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>For a compound of <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G3466 - μυστήριον - mystḗrion - moos-tay'-ree-on/3466\">G3466</a>; to <i>shut down</i>, that is, <i>close</i> the eyes: - close.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}